\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 First of all can you tell me about your family, you know, the number of children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, only me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You were an only child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What was your father's job, you mentioned he was a boot-?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes he was, he was, he used to make all the shoes for these millionaires}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 
\rquote  yachts\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  crews, that used to come up here and when the season came on the
re'd be, oh, ever so many dirty old, drunken old shoe makers, sleeping in our stable you know, and all that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Skilled craftsmen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. While the season was on. Every room in our house was full of shoes - oh they were lovely, they were calf shoes, 
light calf you know, they had pegs (Wooden Nails) in the soles, you know, so that they wouldn't scrape the decks. It was quite a skilled, quite a skilled sort of job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And when was the season?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh well it must have been in the summer I should think because these yachts used to go to the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
Mediterranean{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 For }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  weeks, according to the weather there, and I think perhaps that they were fitted out in the spring.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And your father supervised the other shoemakers you were mentioning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well my father was skilled too, but a bad businessman. When he died, nearly everybody in this village owed him money, he used to say "They will pay me, I know" - he was a lovable character, he was really. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 And he was mostly you know he was very, very friendly with all the yacht skippers and all that, he used to have sessions in pubs. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
I will tell you all about the election and that, later on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 He was happy in his work was he, he enjoyed his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, but he had got a pi
ece of land up here, up this road, over the other side, were and a quarter and that was his relaxation, he didn't do the work, he had it set with marvellous apple trees, Cox's Orange and that, you know, he used to sell the apples you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How far would he sell them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Actually, he had sold them outside our shop, you know, on a stall there. Much to the disgust of the other tradesmen in the village. He had to do it, me were always hard up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you think you were harder up than you would have been had he collected more debts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
He was too kind hearted, he used to lend money to people when he wanted it himself, you know. Never got it back, of course. You can be too easy, can't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, that is quite true. Was he - did you spend a lot of time with him, when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well, yes he use to take me out on Sundays. For walks. And I can even remember at a very early age eating a coconut biscuit in the road and crying while he had a drink, and of course children are not allowed in public houses any more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were they at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They must have been mustn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I wasn't sure about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And he'd take you out most Sundays, would you go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 My brother used to - too
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes we would yes. We w
ould go for a walk in the country and we had friends who had various sandpits and orchards and - a few miles off and we used to visit them. It was a very nice simple life really you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have holidays at all together, did you go away for holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well we used to go to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}, my mother }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 
&}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  I, but you see he couldn't very well leave the business. He used to come down weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Where would you stay when you went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 At a boarding house.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember anything about what you did then, when you were in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}
? What it was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh it was lovely! On the beach. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 
I was the only child from the boarding house and everybody made a frightful fuss of me, you know, took me for donkey rides. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't remember if there were any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10320613\charrsid9112526 P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
ierrots then, perhaps I was too young, but I could play the piano a little bit then and of course they just went off the deep end because I could play the piano, and I was about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 6}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you, when you went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}, did you make friends 
with other children there who were on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think I, I don't remember. Sometimes relatives would come from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Liverpool{\*\xmlclose}
 and bring their children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But on the whole, were you quite a solitary child, or did you spend quite a lot of time with other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, a lot you see, one day when we go down the village street, I will show you where we lived and it was mid - er mid the village, near the school, handy for everybody. Our house was always full, children, and friends dropping in, mus
ical evenings we had and cards and all that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Would people just sort of call in at any time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. Not very many formal invitations. That's why they were so successful I think! Don't you think that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think you are quite right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
I sometimes feel like seeing somebody at a certain time, and not at another. And you go round and make terrific preparations for them if you invite them, don't you, you won't say I'm inhospitable, I'm not!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Not at all, I quite agree with you, it is bad
 that these things have to be so organised sometimes, you know, I think it is marvellous that people can sort of drop in like that. Did your parents have a very wide acquaintance in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Among all classes of people?
