\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well we w
ould go for the evening meal. Well do you know in our house in the High Street there was a beam across the little sitting room and people used to all drift in there just before the Old Year closed and write their initials on this beam.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Now could you describe to me the Christmas, you know, the evening meal? What you would do, and that kind of thing.
