Well, we would have a very nice meal, you know, probably cold turkey and salad and things like that you know. And a hot Christmas pudding afterwards. We always had plenty of drink, believe me! Must have been, you know, pushed through the Customs!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What sort of drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, we used to have ginger beer of course, but they used to drink plenty of whisky really, -
