\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, yes, everything like that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And would the Christmas pudding be carried round the table in flames, like I have sometimes seen in old pictures?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No. It was put on the table and cut.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Just put on the table and cut, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 With custard or cream you know. Most of these people that we went too were a lot better off than we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were they?
