\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, because Father was a poor businessman then!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were you conscious of the fact that they were better off than you? As a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh no, no. They had a much smarter house than we had. But I had rather a knack of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 behaviour}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , I was as good as anybody you know, it is wonderful for an only one isn't it? To be like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you exchange presents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, mostly sweets or books. Boxes of chocolates and things like that.
