\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes. It consisted mostly of singing, everybody could sing, and then we used to, they all stood round the piano and sang and, you know,
