 cottages made into one because it had got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  staircases and my father had the shop built on the front - attics it had, t
