\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 - do you know what }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  are?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I have just heard of them actually - I don't know much about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I had an uncle who was a builder, he was a great }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 S}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7286415\charrsid9112526 wedenborgian}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 and they started the Society here. I don't know quite what I believe you know - isn't it shocking oh? But I was always at the Church of England, at the village church, when I was about, when I left college.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What do the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  believe, what is their faith?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh well there is a lot of it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Too much to tell?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They believe that when you die, you don't go to heaven or hell you go to some sort of society which is akin to you,
 you see. You would feel uncomfortable if you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7286415\charrsid9112526 were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  with too good (?) people wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mean you went to a place where the people were similar to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well was place, you know a sphere.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7286415\charrsid9112526  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you have a Church, a place where -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well we had a building. We had a very nice American organ. Which I played before I became at the Church of England. But you see I was learning - the organ attracted me. That was really dreadful wasn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It attracted you to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, to the Church of England. Because it was a his manual and peel organ you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you go then to both places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 The }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  only had one service a day in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And you would go to the Church of England as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I wouldn't go to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  once I had started the Church of England, I was organist at the Church, because believe me there was quite a lot of controversy about it, in the village you see.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I had anonymous letters - "Go back to your own Church. We don't want you in our Church". I was very young when I was made organist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Let me see. It was during the First War. I can't remember which year it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Sometime in the First War. So you would have been only in your early twenties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Yes. Very early twenties I think. Well do you know that there was the organist who left, she, all the men said that they wouldn't come, in the choir, because I, they wanted an older man in the choir you see, an 
older organist and I went to the Rector and said "Look I don't want to be organist and cause all this disturbance" and he kept sending me letters every day "The Lord is on our side" and we will have our splendid - he was grey and gnarled (?)}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I knew quite a lot of the songs that were about in the music halls
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 On the second Sunday I was there, I had a full choir of men. Fellow who'd come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That had just joined?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, because they knew me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It didn't matter about the others having left then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, and didn't they have a shock when they came to Church!
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What did they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh they used to sing in the Congregation. Oh, then they all decided they would come back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So what happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 There was a row of chairs at the side of the choir stalls so they could all come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They were all allowed to rejoin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. Except one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Why wasn't he allowed to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh they were allowed to but he, I don't think he liked me, I don't know. He thought I was a chit you see, to be playing the organ.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 As well as playing the organ, did you also conduct the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, we had the school master from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13659475\charrsid9112526 Elmstead}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  who was a friend of mine, came over and conducted the choir. I used to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13659475\charrsid9112526 30}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  a year for playing the organ. That wasn't bad was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh but it was a terrific tie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How much of your time did it take up then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh it wasn't so much during the week, we had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  choir practices a week. But it was Sundays, you know, when you wanted to go places.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have anyone to relieve you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes I did have relief. And actually, you know, I taught some of the choir boys to play the organ.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So you had pupils as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I didn't - not paid pupils - but I used to tell them about the stops and that and
 get them to play for the choir practice, when I had the boys alone you see. Well, some of them have become really good organists you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you think that you were the first young woman organist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Young. There was a woman before me. But she was
 an old maid. She was a very charming woman. Until this business came. And I rather suspected that she was the one that kept sending me anonymous letters!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What sort of thing would she say in the anonymous letters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh "We don't want you," Go back to your own Church. \{ILLEGIBLE\} and things like that, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And after that, after you got the job at the Church, did you not go back to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Swedenburgian}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 {\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Church
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I didn't. They closed soon after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Why?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Because the size of the congregations was so sparse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You say your father was one to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 He was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgian}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was it because of his influence that you became one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, it was my uncle really. \{ILLEGIBLE\} He used to have a Sunday School }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 
down }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 at his house. There were a lot of us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or is it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  - how do you say it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians. I don't think they say }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Swedenborgians}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , no, they can't because there is an "I" in it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 There is a church in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}
, and there is a very, very go ahead young person up there called Frank Rose (?), he is Secretary of the Arts Society too, so you know what he is like. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
He is very nice, He has tried to get me to go up there to the service because they want an organist but I am not taking on any mo
re organist jobs. He said he would come down and fetch me! And bring me back. But I really - I have too much to do. I would like to very much...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It's very interesting actually, about the Swedenborgians, and the Church of England as well. Would it have
 been - in your early life, say, would you have gone to the Church or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}England{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Yes, I went to the Sunday School and I was baptised in the Church and my mother was in the choir before she was married. When she first came from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Jersey{\*\xmlclose}.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And were your parents married in the Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know, no, I don't think so. I believe that they were married in the Registry Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then you started going to this uncle's Sunday School and did you go to that as well as the Church of Engl
and one, or did you go drop the Church of England one and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh I had left it then, because I was older you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What age would you have been when you went to the Swedenborgian one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well perhaps ten or eleven or twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You didn't teach, you just were a pupil in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh in it, Uncle Dan (?) used to teach. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 everything in the Bible, it is lovely. You know, the way they, all the parables and that, they have got the spiritual meaning to them.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And you enjoyed it did you, that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes I did. In fact, my dear, I went in for an exam, don't think I am blowing my own trumpet, they had exams you see, all over 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}England{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} and I came out top! Top of all {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}England
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were you excited by that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think so. Uncle Dan was more excited. He gave me a guinea, I remember that!
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 To be frank did you have a fairly good idea of your own intelligence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well I don't think I ever thought much of myself really,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, but being an only one, you don't you know, do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know, because I am not an only one. Do you mean you didn't think much about yourself as compared with other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. But then I found out when I was in an exam or anything, I was always very good. And I had a friend who was always very good too. T}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 he wife of this man who went to the front}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
. She was a Congregationalist but she came to, she came to the Swedenborgian Sunday School and she came from next on the list. They all read our papers afterwards, Uncle Dan had some f
riends in, some Swedenborgian friends, and they read them all and they all decided that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 Win\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 paper was better than mine. So they all had a shock when it came round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 How }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 about, how many other children went, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 To the Sunday School? Oh about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
. I have got some lovely photographs, somewhere among my snap shots, taken in our garden. We all had those frilly silk hats on your know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And you then went back to the Church of England one did you, or did you stop?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, but I wil
l tell you how I started sing to the Church of England, by having all the lessons off this woman you see. Then when she didn't want to get up for early service she used to ask me if I would go and play for the early service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, and that's now you gradually went back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. I was never may decided about religion. Not mean was the same, I think that she drifted with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And your father, was he decided, or did he change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 No, father was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  Swedenborgian, well what he did believe. He was really
 quite a good man you know. A bit wild, but still, there you are, he always used to be a heavy drinker you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 More for the fun of the thing you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And of course he associated with sailors a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. Or captains you know. Engineers - and always used to go in public houses - all morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 All the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But only at certain times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When they were open, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What every morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 He would work in the afternoon and evening, then, would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't remember when he worked! Well when he did work he worked very hard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Your mother, can you tell me something about her, and her life, was she a very busy person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Very capable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Very pretty. And knew how to dress. Small. And French looking, you know. But she wouldn't}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  be bound to the house,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 she would go out you see. Colchester or Clacton, but in the end, Father didn't want to go out anywhere very much, and I sometimes think that I have got like him this winter, I mustn't you know. You mustn't stick in the house all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You find it harder and harder to go out I think if you do stay in a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 You know I haven't enough to go and buy new clothes but I am going next week.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 On your own?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. I must go and have a session in Colchester, if not in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}. I have a friend, a}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  cousin}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  who lives at Romford and well she came down }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  weeks ago and they grumbled}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  me horribly about my appearance. Very smart they are. I go up to her and we shop in Romford sometimes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you? I have only passed through }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 here the in trains. I have never been there. When you were a child, did you go shopping for clothes, with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you often go out shopping and doing things with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 
She had got a terrific sense of humour you know I have got ever such a big head. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 I have got a big}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  head too actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It doesn't look big.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It is though, it is funny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Perhaps you have got more at the back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Apart from hair, I have got a big head.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
I have too, I have got mine across there! When we used to go and get me a hat, because everybody had to have hats in those days, it always seemed that they brought me the smallest one in the shop! Oh my mother and I, we used to have fits of laughter!

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, we were noisy girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember how your mother did her shopping for everyday things like food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh we were amid - absolutely amongst all the shops. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 The butchers just ov
er the road, the grocer's next door.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did your mother go to the shop and choose the things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They didn't call round with things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh well, it was only a step you see. I don't think that they called round so much in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did they not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Perhaps in the town area they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But she did that herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 She was a very good cook too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was she. Did she enjoy cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you tell me something about the sort of food that you had in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 We had very good food, because, the meat was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 marvellous}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  in those days wasn't it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 My father had a friend over at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Crockleford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , a farmer and butcher and we always used to have lovely beef from him you see. We had lots of rabbits and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  hares}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  and game which I detested because pap}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  used to go out shooting a lot.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526  
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You'd get what he had at his shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you have meat twice a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No. Only for the mid-day meal perhaps we might have a little for breakfast, I don't know. I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You can't remember what you had for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No. Perhaps an egg, or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember what else you had for breakfast? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 Those}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  are really very important things to know about because they are such social things usually
, one spends so much time over them. I wonder if you could sort of describe breakfast to me? Would you all sit down together for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, there were only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  of us you see. I think we had porridge perhaps sometimes. Or boiled eggs, or egg and bacon. I don't remember ever having anything else I don't think we ever had fish for breakfast. But sometimes we would go on the }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 Quay}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  and buy a beautiful }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 bend}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  of fresh fish for 6d.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 A beautiful what did you say?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Bend of fish, you know. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bend{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} of fish
 is fish all put together on a wire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, I have never heard the term.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Haven't you - it might be {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Essex{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It might be, or it might be a very fishing sort of area term. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, and sometimes we would have, sometimes we would have them for mid-day dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Or perhaps for tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And for breakfast, would you have something to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Always tea. Never coffee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember when you were a small child, would you have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 had}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  tea to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't remember,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you have bread, that sort of thing, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 marmalade}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Bread and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10100668\charrsid9112526 marmalade}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  and jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then your mother would serve that meal would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you help her at all with the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 She did it all herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Yes. We used to have properly laid tables with serviettes, linen serviettes you know. We called them serviettes, they don't know, do they? What do they call them, napkins, now don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well I think they call them both don't they, some people think it's smarter to say napkins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And serviettes with a ring, you know, we always had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, would you, you would each have your own ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you have a table cloth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes. Always white.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did your mother attach importance to table settings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was she somebody who cared about the appearance of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes, yes. Very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have Grace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Only when we had visitors!
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You're the second person who has said that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Especially my uncle, when he came, the Swedenborgian.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. Who would say Grace on these occasions? Did your mother say it or did your father say it, the Grace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh the uncle I am afraid. If }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 Momma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  or Poppa had said it we might have laughed! Dreadful people really! But it is funny, if we had a very nice dinner, hare, or something like that, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 Momma}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  would go down to her sister, the wife of the builder and say you must come up tomorrow because we are going to have so and so, and they would come up, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 She would especially invite them because it was something nice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That wasn't your Swedenborgian uncle that one? So he'd come up and he would say Grace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 We used to have pudding you know. First. For the first course. A boiled {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Yorkshire{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes I have heard about those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And fill them, up, fill people up with those before the meat comes on. And of course we had Yorkshire pudding in turn(?).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Would you have the boiled {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Yorkshire{\*\xmlclose} - that is just flour and water isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And egg.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And egg, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It comes out lovely and light you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Would you have that just on its own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, with gravy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have any other kind of puddings as well, before the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15548582\charrsid9112526 Things like the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  boiled {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Yorkshire
{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well if we had it you know, dumplings in soup.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But you didn't always have it before your mid-day meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 About how often would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was it more often than not, do you think, perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What are your talking about now, the pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 The pudding before the meat. I am very interested in this because it is something which seems to have gone out, very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well you have it, we had it if we had a baked dinner you see. Or roast dinne
r. Sometimes we used to have a joint on the spit in front of the fire, you know. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That must have been delicious!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. And I can remember my mother never, never, put things like Bisto in to make gravy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That's perhaps because she was half French.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know, but she got lovely gravy without putting of in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I know, you can. Was it a point of principle with her not to put it in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh well, she would say "Rubbish" you see. "This old}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526  \{ILLEGIBLE\}}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  stuff, rubbish" you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was her range of different dishes quite wide, that she would cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think so. We used to have meat pudding and meat pie and rabbit pie and roast -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was she good at pastry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. And you know, roast joints and roast rabbit, we used to have roast rabbit, and hare, jugged hare and chickens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And fish? You said you would get a bend of fish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, fried they would be, fried.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 She didn't bake fish?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then would you have pudding, afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, well, fruit or something like that. You know. Perhaps a fruit pie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You didn't have any other kinds of puddings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well we had the fruit, but not made custard, egg custard. Egg custard either baked or done in a saucepan. Have you ever heard of it done in a saucepan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I mean ordinary runny custard I have done in a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526  saucepan}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 With egg?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And not with custard powder?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I always make mine with an egg! Because I think it tastes much nicer, we don't have it very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then would you drink anything with your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well water.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you ever have beer or wine with the food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Not as a child. No. I expect they had beer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But you didn't have it at family meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then in the evening, what would be your last meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh we would have tea, and that was about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 17}}}5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  o'clock{\*\xmlclose}
. You might have had a cup of milk or something like that when you were young, when I was young, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Would you have had tea with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh yes yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And what would you have had to eat }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  tea when you were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh I used to have bread and butter and jam and a kind of paste, and sardines, or we used to have sardines sometimes. And cake. Or tart.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Tea to drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. But not, not high tea you know, just those things you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What some people call "cold tea".
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Nothing hot?
