\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And when you recited, did you ever recite in a chorus? Group recitations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think we did. But she was really very good at speech, you know. We all spoke well when we were doing these things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did she think that important, the way the girls spoke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, very, yes. Very important.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Right through the school, even the younger girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And was she interested in the manners of the girls, and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did she have much contact with the parents
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well, no. They've never had much contact with the parents in Wivenhoe. There's been no Parent Teachers Association, and when ... Mr. Thomas is nice, isn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I've never met him, actually. I will when Stephen goes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 He lived in Wivenhoe, lives here now. I have taught there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What, at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Bentley{\*\xmlclose} 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}School{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But why do you think the Wivenhoe one at that time didn't have much to do with parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I don't think they did anywhere, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I get the impression they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Because, I think the only time they had anything to do with parents was when the parents came down to complain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did this happen much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, not in her time, but
 I taught here, you know, before I retired, but not the last few years 'cos I was with ... I'd rather be under a headmaster anyhow. But there was a headmistress there who just wouldn't see people. She was a tartar really, and I only stuck it because it wa
s where I was living, and I could do the music, and I was near my mother, you see. I could ... my mother lived in one of the houses where her back garden over-looked the playground, and I could see her about 3 or 4 times a day, you see, so I stuck it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 I should have asked you, could you give my any kind of idea of your parents' date of birth? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How much older were they than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Papa was ... I think he was 8 years older than }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 Mamma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , and I think I was born when she was about 28.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And to get back to the school again, can you remember anything else about the school, particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Music, I think. We used to read from sight, turn it into tonic solfa. And we used to do crowds of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 -part songs, which was good, wasn't it. I expect we did some of those in ... this little head \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 was so good at English, he was very good at music, too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you sing from sight, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They did, yes, yes, they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. And I taught it, too, when I ... before I retired, was commended by the Inspector for their wonderful sight reading.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did all the girls in the school learn to sing by sight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, of course some of them who are tone deaf you have to day, 'be quiet for a bit, dear, while we do this'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember anything else, physical recreation, and that sort of thing Drill, did you do anything of that kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 We used to do dancing, yes. I don't think ... it wasn't country or folk dancing, I don't know what it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Could it have been what they call 'rhythmics', rather more modern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no. That came in later, 'cos I taught that, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I was just trying to think what sort of dancing it was, if it wasn't folk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, things like the Highland Fling, like that, you know. And tripping, you know and all that. They always used to have a May Queen there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 At the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, voted in by the girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did they have a ceremony then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, and all the maids of honour had to trip, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did they have a maypole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, not a maypole.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you tell me more about the May Queen one. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 
Why was the girl chosen May Queen?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, chiefly through popularity with the girls, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And was she always in the top form?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think so. Yes, I think she was. We used to vote on little scraps of paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did the whole school vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I've never heard of this before, do you think it was common?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They have them still, don't they? On the other side of ... I taught mostly in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} and {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}... But the other side of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
Colchester{\*\xmlclose} they have them, and they do have maypoles there. There were pictures in the local papers the other day of ... I forget now where it was, Copford, or somewhere there, you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They had a may queen in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. In the playground, this was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And everyone had a vote, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did the teachers vote too, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did they dress up? Tell me something about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well, they ... you know, they were just decked out with flowers, you know, and perhaps a crown on their head.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did they have anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no, no, it was in the school session, you see. But before we went to school on that day the May ladies used to come round to our doors.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you tell me about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
There would be at least 3 and the middle one would stand in a hoop decorated with flowers, and they would be all trimmed up with flowers, and they used to knock on the door, you see ... shall I sing it to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, please do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 <poem>}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
"Please remember the May Lady, My father has gone to sea, My mother has gone to fetch him, Please remember me."</poem>. And one of them would say 'Coo coo, Coo coo' and then, you see, you would give them a penny and they would go away.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I'm so glad somebody else is interested in these things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think it's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 marvellous}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 . Well, it's a vanished life, or do they still do it in Wivenhoe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, they haven't done it for years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When did that stop, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 If you've any idea it would be very interesting to know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I haven't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you think you know anyone who could give you any idea about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What a pity I didn't ask my friend to come down, she might remember the date better than I can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It would be interesting to know. You couldn't remember when you last heard that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I couldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you associate it with your very early childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No. Listen, have I heard it since I moved back to .... 'cos I lived in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Surrey{\*\xmlclose}
 when I was first married. I've been back in Wivenhoe for 34 years and I did hear it then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Since you've been back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you tell me who the women were that came round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 They were school children. They were trying to get some pennies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I see. And did lots of groups go round in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 s?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, I don't know, I expect there were rivals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you ever do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no. My father and mother wouldn't let me do anything like that. Or go round }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 arol singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Why wouldn't they like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Some silly sort of pride, I suppose, going round after pennies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It was the money thing that they didn't like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And were there always 3? The girls in a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 threesome}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 ?
