\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And why was this, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well, I think it was because of the reading I'd done at home, for one thing. My father was a great one for buying up secondhand things, and he bought up 2 or 3 trunkloads of books
, which was pushed up into the attic. And I went up there, and ... you know, when I was alone, and I found a volume of Shakespeare and I tried 60}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 , kind of go}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 t out the plots in my mind, from reading the dialogue, you know, and ... I don't say ... I didn't ever get them outright, but it was a good help to me, wasn't it, trying to get by myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did your parents read aloud to you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When I was very little they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Tell me some of the games you remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, the great ... it was a ga
mbling game, really, that we used to play, and we never ... all the games I can think of we used to play on the ground. Beads, the girls used to play and the boys used to play marbles. Make a hole in the ground ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 This is beads?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. You'd say }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 up - perhaps there'd be 7 playing - and the first one who got one in the hole would pick up all the beads, and bowl them all up, you see. And if one went in the hole, she would then clip the other beads in and take them. And if she didn't tip them in, sh
e didn't take them, you see. And I'd say some of the girls got beads with ... I don't know if you'd know what size they'd been would they? ... Glass beads, you know, various colours, all the same size.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did they wear them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, they'd wear them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did the girls ever play marbles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I never did. The boys used to play, and they used to have a hole in the ground. I don't know how they played it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You don't remember girls ever playing marbles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And boys playing beads?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you think that marbles were played in the same way that beads were played?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well, now, I don't think so. I think they used to have something where one marble hit another, I'm not sure. And then we used to play hopscotch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What type of hopscotch did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, we used to mark it on the ground, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What did it look like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It looked like aitches, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 In a sort of square pattern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, and you ... oh, first of all you did it with 2 feet and then you did it, hop with one foot, and all sorts of variations like that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
It's curious you should mention hopscotch because I don't think I've seen a hopscotch written around since I've been down this part. I used to see them in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}London{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}. Do you think it's going out of fashion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Well, I haven't seen it for years, and ... oh, when I came back to work and I taught round here in various schools, I didn't see any children playing it round here. We used to play ... all our games we used
 to play sitting on the ground. Perhaps there was grass, I don't know. 'I sent a letter to my love', do you know that one? 'and on the way I dropped it. One of you has picked it up and put it in his pocket'. 'It isn't you, it isn't you, it isn't you, it i
s you' and when you touched the person, 'it is you', they immediately got up and chased you, you see, and you tried to get in their place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Any others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I can't think of it now, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you remember any sort of 'picks', you know, when you go
 to see who's going to be 'on', or 'it', or whatever you call it, and you pick round in a ring saying a rhyme? Do you know what I mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, that was more or less that, wasn't it? 'Cos they'd all be sitting in a ring, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you play much with balls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes. Oh, that ... we used to play rounders, but we mistakenly called it baseball, peculiarly enough. I don't know why.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you play with a bat? A bat to hit the ball with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, yes. Or any old bit of wood we could get, you kn
ow. Well, we didn't have any equipment ... much equipment for playing games at school, we just had to make it up, you see. And do you know ... we were talking about dancing, do you know, I had never ... I had quite a lot to do with folk dancing and all th
at, and playing for them and all that, you know, but I've never come across an Essex folk dance.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Have you ever heard of one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I haven't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Or an {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Essex{\*\xmlclose} folk song?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, that's an interesting point. I asked an old man in Ardleigh if he kn
ew any folk songs and he said no, they'd only sung religious songs when he was a child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 There are no songs that you can remember people singing that you think are peculiarly {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Essex
{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't, no. I've racked my brains, and ... let me see, now ... certainly no folk dances. And the folk dance revival didn't come to 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose} until I was out of college and I was dragged into it because I used to play for them, you see, and I used to go to the classes. What year would that be - oh, about 1914. 1913 or 
'14. But of course, I mean, there were dancing ... folk dancers all over {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}England{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, weren't there, every year. But they didn't come to 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Essex{\*\xmlclose}. A man came from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Devonshire{\*\xmlclose}, a headmaster and I think he brought it to Essex.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What did you remember about the food? Was it the food you had in your own home when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes, talking about puddings, I've got to tell you about boiled suet puddings, that we had sometimes with gravy instead of 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Yorkshire{\*\xmlclose}. My word that was a good standby, wasn't it!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know. I'm afraid I owe my bulk partly to it, though (laughter). But my mother }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\ul\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 never }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 used any kind of gravy salt, or anything like that, you know, and of course, I expect it did really taste nice with this pudding. A very l
ight boiled pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did she use herb and garlic, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, she was very fond of garlic. We used to have garlic in meat puddings, and steak and kidney puddings. And she used to ... we used to grow herbs in the garden, marjoram and thyme and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did people who came and had meals with you, did they things of the food as being a bit unusual, having garlic in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did other people use garlic at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, the only one I can think of was m
y uncle, the builder, because, you see, my mother and her sisters were all brought up in Jersey, you know, and of course they use a lot of garlic in Jersey, and it grows in the commons there, wild. You asked if we went for holidays, but my mother and I we
nt to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Jersey{\*\xmlclose} }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 or 3 times. My father couldn't leave the business, you see. He would go away for a few days on his own, sometimes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What would he do on his holiday, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, actually, he used to meet his schoolmaster brother from the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Midlands{\*\xmlclose} an
d ... I don't know what they did. I expect they drank plenty of beer! (laughter) And ate a lot of food, and all the rest of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did they have any sort of sport? You know, shooting ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, not on holidays. My father was very keen on shooting. A
nd my uncle, the schoolmaster, he was very good at all kinds of sport, quoits and everything like that, you know. And musical, he was. He was a great man, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can I go back to what you were telling me about your education. I think we more of less 
covered all the points we could think of about that school that you went to - you know, the very good school, which was really an Elementary school, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, that's what it was called, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then you told me that you left and went to the Pupil-Teacher's Centre, is that right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, well ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 In {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Not as a pupil-teacher. If you were a bit gifted and clever at school you didn't get a chance to get a scholarship at the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 G}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 rammar }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 S}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
chool like there were for boys in those days, but they dragged you into the teaching profession, you see. Well anyhow, we went up there, my friend and I and I suppose we were good, you know, at our work, and after we'd been there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  years it became a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 H}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
igh }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637746\charrsid9112526 S}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 chool in the old building, but it was ca
lled a high school, that's where the rep. is now. And people who weren't any good were tipped out, then, and the others were kept on - what was it, for a year? - we became student teachers then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But did you all become student teachers, every one in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Everybody that was kept on, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So you know it was called a high school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no, when it was called a high school it was different then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So when it was called a high school you were still there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But you continued as a student teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. We went up to the school one day a week, and we had to specialize in a subject, you see. I specialized in English.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But before you went out one day a week, how many years were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think it must have been 3.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
That's what you said last week, I think. And what sort of difference was there in the kind of schooling you got there from what you got in Wivenhoe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well, they were all ... not any of them were general teachers, you see, they all specialized in their own subject, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What subjects did you do there, can you remember? In those 3 years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well, we did lots of maths. Very clever maths master, we had. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526 g}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 eography - I wasn't very good at geography; and history, and science! We d
id no end of science. The laboratory there did experiments and all sorts of things, you know. We had a good general education there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have any languages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, French, yes, not anything else. But French.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, I loved French.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did your mother speak French?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 A little bit, yes, the patois, you know. But when we went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Jersey{\*\xmlclose}
 all my relations could speak both and ... you know, they were very religious and one of them was a local preacher. He used to go round and preach to the various chapels. I suppose he preached in the patois, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When you went to the school, the pupil}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526 /}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  teachers centre, how many of you went out of your year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 .

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Only you and your friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Good Gracious, and not any more went for years and years!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was it considered an honour, then, to have gone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, yes. It was like ... it was the same as winning a free scholarship to the Grammar School. We had all our expenses paid, travel fares and books and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And can you remember how you heard that you were going to go? Can you remember the moment you were told?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't, no. The only thing I can remember was when my son passed the 11-plus, how I wept.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But when you went to this new schoo
l, did you already have it in your mind that you knew you were going to be a teacher? At that stage of your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When did you first realise you were going to be a teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, when we passed the thing, you see, when we passed to go up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But I mean, has it ever occurred to you to have any other kind of profession?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
No, you couldn't, my dear, we were very restricted here. That was the only thing that anybody with brains could do, really. 'Cos, I mean, there were no jobs for girl secretaries, or even typists and shorthand people then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
And do you think for some time before you went to the school you'd sort of thought that you were going to be a teacher, or didn't you think much about it 'till you heard you were passing up to the new school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, I don't know. I know an inspector came down and questioned us and said, 'why do you want to be a teacher?' and my friend gave a very clever answer, she said, 'I'm very fond of children'. I thought, 'oh, good heavens, what 
can I say?' and when he said it to me, I said, 'my parents wish me to'. I'd got teachers in my family, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you meet girls from lots of different places when you went to this new school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, just round, you know. Just round {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}
. Copford and Dovercourt and places like ... and {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Clacton{\*\xmlclose}. Oh, it was quite ... enlarging our acquaintances, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you meet in any way different types of girls from what you'd met before You know, in class, or anything, or were they much the same?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, they were a bit more intellectual, anyhow - or intelligent. Bit more intelligent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did you join in any things - activities in the town at all? Did you join any sort of town societies, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose} societies, when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 While we were there they had the Colchester Pageant. A }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 marvellous}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  affair by Louis M. Parker. It lasted a fortnight, you know, and they had the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Castle{\*\xmlclose} 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Park{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} and ... well, we were in ... I was in the fishergirls' dance. Oh, it was lovely, really, to be in ther
e, you know, and have Louis Parker speaking to us through a loud speaker, and all. But we didn't ... well the only thing we played tennis, but it was our own club, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 For the school, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you feel that you sort of got to know a new town, at all? I mean did it make any difference to your feeling about 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}, do you think, going to school in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You just went to school and then came back again, and that was that, really
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well ... we didn't .... there were no pictures to go to then, you see, and ... well sometimes we'd go to a party of a girl in 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Colchester{\*\xmlclose}, or something like that. We went to parties. And of course, actually, during that time I was in ... we had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 marvellous}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  concert party in Wivenhoe, and I was pianist for that, you see. I was about 14 then, 14 or 15 and, you know, you get a lot of fun in that kind of thing, don't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And how did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Train. No other way than train. And believe me, there was something going on in the train going up there, you know, we had awful fun, really.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What did you get for pocket money at that time, do you remember? Did you get any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, I'm sure I did, I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you ever earn any money when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
I remember you said that on the May Day, your parents wouldn't have liked you to go round like that. You never had a holiday job, or did a paper round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No. Well, children didn't in those day
s, you know, going up to school or the grammar school. They didn't do it. They didn't have a paper round, or anything. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And can you tell me how it was when you started being a student teacher? Did you start teaching in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, observing a bit and I was teaching down here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That was at the elementary school here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I was first of all sent to the infants' and I wouldn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Because the headmistress at the infants' was a real old cat (laughter). And they transferred me 
to the girls' school where I had been before, you see. I'm afraid I wasn't a very good teacher then. I hadn't a lot of confidence in myself, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So how long did you just observe? Did you start teaching quite soon?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, perhaps a week and then, perhaps, we'd have one lesson, you see, and the headmistress would come and watch us teach.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Would she give you some help in preparing the lesson?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes. And plenty of criticism afterwards. Just like having your lessons giving you criticism lesson in the training times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then one day a week you went back to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What was it like going back to school for one day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, lovely. You see, we were each allowed to do kind of research into the subject we'd chosen, you se
e, going to the library, and also going to the lectures at the library. What did they call those? Extension lectures, you know. University }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526 E}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 xtension lectures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What university would that have been, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 London, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How often were they held?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Once a week. For a course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And was there any exam at the end of the course, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember the subject of any of the lectures that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Writers of the something century. Now the century ... that was the one where Smollett came in... Was that 16}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\super\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  Century, or 17}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I think it's 17}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , actually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And all the rather questionably moral writers, you know. They said things so plainly
, didn't they? Believe me, we loved that! (laughter) We were good little girls, though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you go on your own, or were you taken by a teacher to these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, we went on our own. It was just down ... from where the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526  R}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 ep. is down to the Castle Park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How old would you have been then? About 17, would you? When you came back one way a week as a student teacher?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So for how long did you continue coming back one day a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Only for a year. And then we went to College, you see, to Bishops Stortford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you tell me about what it was like there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, I think it was a Church college, you see, and I was a Nonconformist, so I was not allowed to sleep in the college, much to our enjoyment because we had an annexe about 5 minutes
' walk from the college - some villas knocked together and believe me, that was a lovely time! What we did in that time I couldn't tell you, but anyhow ... You see, if we weren't at the college they'd say, 'oh, they're at the annexe' so nobody quite knew 
where we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And were you quite unchaperoned in your annexe, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, no, there was a very nice lady superintendent. She was very fond of Wynn and me. Used to ask us to her house to ... up to her room for tea and all the rest of it. And she had to tell us off once, she said 'You know, you girls are ... you }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 girls, I'm very fond of you ...' Don't think we were wicked, we weren't. She said, 'but you're going to get me the sack' (laughter) 'Cos we'd stayed out late, and we knew a few bank clerks near, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And you used to go out in the evenings with them, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 If we could, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And was that really not permitted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no!!! I told you how I was nearly ... we were both nearly sent down the first week we were there because t
here was a girl who came from a neighbouring village - I think she used to go home for weekends - and she invited us to her house to tea and her brother walked home with us to Bishops Stortford and there was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\ul\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 fearful}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  outcry about that! (laughter) You just think of that now. Students having fellows in their bedrooms, don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were you punished for having walked home with him, or was there simply a row?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, simply a row.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were you actually ever allowed to go out at night with a young man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, no! Unless your parents wrote and unless it was your acknowledged boyfriend, you see, and then you were. We had a most lovely Principal, he had been senior \{ILLEGIBLE\} at Cambridge, the Rev. Larry Ainsley, and he used to live somewhere near. Oh, do 
you know, poor old thing, he used to give us Divinity lectures, and all the girls were doing crochet work or knitting in the back, and if he by any chance should walk from the front of the room to the back, you'd hear a frightful clang of knitting pins fa
l
ling on the floor. We thought that was wicked. Isn't it funny, you know, the different standard now. We used to have very nice dramatic performances there, too. We did 'Electra' once - you can't imagine me as a Grecian chorus lady, posing, can you? (laugh
ter) And then the staff got up a play once, and I was a cook in it, and ... which was the other one we had? One of Shakespeare's ... 'Twelfth Night'.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What part did you have in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I can't remember. Something very unimportant, anyhow. Whatever was I? A very small part, I know. I wasn't very good on the stage, really.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When you went to the college, did you have many lessons or lectures about education and psychology, that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes! We had a most wonderful psychology lecturer
. I've still got the notes somewhere and you've heard of Sir Luke Fyles, the artist, have you? Sir Luke Fyles? Well, it was his niece. Oh, she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13196036\charrsid9112526 marvellous}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , you know, you just sat spellbound when she started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And then what other educational things did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Nature study; and English - I was very disappointed in the English mistress because English was my subject and I didn't like her. And we had very nice music lessons, at which I was the accompanist again. And what else did we ...? Oh, we h
ad some P.T., yes. Of course, we had P.T. twice a week, you know, in gym slips.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have apparatus and ropes and buck and horse and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no. No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What sort of P.T. was it, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, it included 
dancing, too. You know, quite ordinary, arms bending and stretching and doing things on the floor and all that kind of thing. Very similar to what they ... it had just started, you see ... what they do in schools now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you enjoy doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And it was quite new at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
I think it was, yes. We'd never done any in the school down here before. I went there. It's a long time to remember, you know. We had a very nice P.T. mistress, very ... you know, lively and all the rest of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How many years were you at Bishops Stortford?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And of those }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  years how much of the time did you spend teaching in school? You know, teaching practice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I believe we had to do about 6 weeks altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember anything about those 6 weeks, where you went and what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Yes. First of all I went to the ... there was a practicing school attached to the college and the headmistress there was, to put it plainly, a bitch. She was, really. You know, she'd say to the chi
ldren that you were teaching, 'now children, answer up nicely because I want to give this student a good mark'. Did you ever know anything so horrible!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How terrible!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Wasn't it? To say it to the children, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When you say it was a practice school, it was an ordinary school, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But simply it received these trainee teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Yes. And we also went to other schools in Bishops Stortford which were vastly different, you know, especially ... you know, if you get a mixed school it was so different, we were treated so differently.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mean by 'mixed', boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. I got a good mark in that, but I didn't at the practicing school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How many schools did you go to altogether, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , I th
ink, I can't remember any other. But, you know, I had my revenge on her. I went on a P.T. course}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526  at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Balliol College at North Wales one day and she was up there, all teeth, you know, and came up to me because we were among the lowly and said, 'Oh, this is Miss Jermyn, how are you?' I said, 'I'm afraid I don't remember you'. I jolly well }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \ul\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  remember. She gave me some miserable times. So she did lots of the girls, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 She was the headmistress of this school, was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. There were one or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  assistants and they were very nice, too, and very sympathetic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What type of school was it? An elementary school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, and Church because, you see, the college was Church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 That was something I don't think I asked you last week, was the Wivenhoe one a Church school, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, not when I was there. Previously I believe it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have any contact with the Bishops Stortford College, at all? The boys' school, or wasn't that there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no. My dear, it was on a definitely hig
her plane than our college. 16 was, you know, we were only scrubbing teachers, you see, but they ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you know somebody who went there, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, my husband was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Not in my time, of course. There isn't now. I don't think there is now any contact.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Is there not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I don't think so. Because, you see, they are at the other end of Bishops Stortford, for one thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have any contact with any other sort of institution for boys, or any dances, for example, with a boys' college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Nothing like that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I know they do now, of course, don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But you didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Tell me about how you met the bank clerks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, because we passed their digs. And they started off by saying 'good
 morning' and that sort of thing, you see. And one Sunday my friend and I went to Cambridge with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 of them, ooh, in fear and trembling. We went to hear the service at .. what's the college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 King's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 In King's College, in the afternoon. We were terribly frightened we were going to be found out. There were rumours, you know, but ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mean for a whole day you left the college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I think ... yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But it was quite daring, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It was.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Weren't there any check-ups during the day as to what the girls were doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Not on Sundays, no. Because, you see, sometimes the girls' parents came down and then, at the annexe we always used to make our own teas on Sunday, you know, have a kind of little gathering there, and nobo
dy quite knew where we were, but we didn't dare to do it more than once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you enjoy it, the day you went to Cambridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes! Specially the music in King's College. Quite near to Cambridge Bishops Stortford, isn't it? \{ILLEGIBLE\} by train, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You went by train, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, there was no other way, was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have bicycles? When you were in college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, one of our friends had a bicycle which we borrowed occasionally, but we didn't ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Boyfriend, or girlfriend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Girlfriend. And we didn't bother to take our own bicycles, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But you had one of your own at home, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes, always had a bicycle. And then you could ride along the lovely country roads and smell the carnations ... the p
inks in the gardens, which you couldn't do now, could you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did the bank clerks write letters to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, no, no. I don't remember, anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And when you left the training college, where did you go after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I was sent to a most awful school hear Southend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How old would you have been then? I'm just trying to think what the date would have been, when you left your college.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 1913.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You left in 1913?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. And I was ... the Essex ... jobs were scarce then, you kno
w, and they sent me to Southend. Oh, no, first of all I went to Elmstead for a few months, on uncertificated pay, and then they sent me to Southend to a place called }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10320613\charrsid9112526 Eastwood}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , just outside Southend. Oh, what a school! Full of dirty gypsies.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How were you on uncertificated pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Because it was the only job I could get for a few weeks, you see, 'till they found this other one for me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can you remember what the pay was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, very little. And when I went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11293696\charrsid9112526 Eastwood}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 , I had to pay digs out of it. It was 30/- a week, or a bit less, perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mean that was your pay, and you had to pay digs out of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What were your digs like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Lovely. I was lodging with a market gardener and his wife, a childless couple, and they ... oh
, they made an awful fuss of me, you know. They got a piano ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mean they got a piano specially for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, they'd got one there and because I could play they liked me all the better for that ... and, I mean, she was such a dear, she even us
ed to wash my hair and all that kind of thing for me, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did she feed you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. They didn't have meals at the schools then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you have all your meals at her home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was the food nice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was it similar sort of food to what you'd been used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And were her manners and ways like what you were used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, yes, you know. She used to let me have my friends there to tea, and I got friendly with some maiden ladies in the place and they u
sed to .. we used to walk into Westcliff to the Dickens Society's performances, you know, and walk back in the dark. Dear, oh, dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How far was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 miles. And I was terrified because it was a bungalow I slept in and I was afraid to open my window at night because of all these gypsies about, you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Were there a great many gypsies about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 There was a gypsy encampment about a mile from where I was lodging.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And did all the gypsy children go to this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, all that cou
ldn't get out of it, you know. They used to come to school in frock coats, you know, and old coats that somebody had given them. Poor little boys about 10 looked like men, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What did the girls wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you find this very difficult, this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well, it was, yes, but I got round to it, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 What class did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16648430\charrsid9112526 can't}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
 remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You were in charge of a whole form?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And to teach them everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 There was one very nice teacher there, a maiden lady. They were all worried about my soul.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Was it a Church of England school, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, but she was ... what was she? Was she a Congregationalist? I don't know, but in Southend we looked up some old Jersey rela
tions and he was ... the man had got a business in London - they were rather well off - and they were Plymouth Brethren.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Do you know what the Plymouth Brethren are like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You mustn't mention the word 'tennis' on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And on
e day, once upon a time the elder boy of the brothers alive went to the bandstand at Westcliff on a Sunday night, and it was broadcast all through the ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How many other teachers were there at the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, I can remember }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190155\charrsid9112526 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 . One was this very nice lady who occasionally asked me to her house in Westcliff, and the other one was a nice girl, too. She was organist at the church -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Where's that place where Anne Boleyn used to live, near there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I don't know, I'm afraid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 About 3 miles out of Eas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11293696\charrsid9112526 two}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 od. I know I cycled there one morning to hear her playing the organ at Church and that kind of thing. I used to come home when I could afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 How often could you get home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, perhaps once a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you get any extra money from your home at all, or did you just live on your salary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, I had to live on my salary. My dear, it was good money in those days. You don't realise that, do you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 This was the job where you were certificated pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. People would say to me, 'you've earning terrifically good money, aren't you'.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes, I suppose you were, especially comparing you with other girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And men. Not many working men were earning 30/- a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 When you went back to Wivenhoe, did you keep up with yo
ur old friends that you'd had at school, or had you not had many friends beside your ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
Oh, yes, we were all friendly, you know. And also, I mean, the other friends in Colchester and other places, they used to come to Wivenhoe, especially the Bright
lingsea girls. They'd come to Wivenhoe and, you know, have a jolly good high tea and go for walks and all that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You didn't feel that you grew apart from them by going away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And that fact that you'd had more education than your old schoolfellows, though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, well, most of them, you see, had - I'm thinking about the Brightlingsea girls - they had the same as I had, except the college.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I see, they'd been on at the school with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Why hadn't they gone on to the college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Possibly because their parents couldn't afford it and they'd got to earn money. They didn't get grants then, you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Your parents had to pay your training college fees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. They weren't very heavy, but for every Distinction you got in Preliminary Certificate, as they called it, they took }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 5 off the fees.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you get any distinctions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes. I always got English and Music. My parents weren't very well off, you know, it was a ... well, I mean, you've got to keep a girl i
n clothes, haven't you, too, you see. Some of my friends were children of big families.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
When you started working, did you feel very different? I mean from the fact that you were supporting yourself. Can you remember having any different feelings or opinions about life and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
No, I didn't, no. I kept longing to be home again and my mother longed for me to be home and ... sew, she said, 'I can always keep on making you blouses and things'. She used to make my clothes very, very clev
erly. Not suits, of course, I used to have a tailor-made suit, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You were homesick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you meet types of people that you hadn't met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I remember when I first started teaching it completely changed my acquaintance
 with society. I met all sorts of types of people I'd not met before, particularly the children. I wondered if this happened to you at all, if you felt that ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, there were the gypsy children, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Gypsy children and the kind spinsters w
ho were so nice to me, but, you know, nothing very exciting. But I didn't stay there very long. Now when did I go? In the October. I think I was only at Elmstead a month and then I applied for a post in Colchester.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 But after you went to Elmstead you went to Southend, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 And how long were you at Southend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Only 'till the February.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 February 1914, would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 So that was how many months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Oh, 4 or 5.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Did you leave that post earlier than you'd intended to leave it, because of the gypsies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 No, I was dying to get out of it all the time. You see, I applied to Colchester and they took me on at once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 You wanted to get back to your home area, was that why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 Well, all my friends were round there. 'Cos, I mean, I did ... they had got a hockey club at Eas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11293696\charrsid9112526 two}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 
od and I played once or twice for them, you know, but ... well, it wasn't quite the same. And then I got this post and I was sent to a school in Colchester that's the Wilson }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11293696\charrsid9112526 Marriage}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526  School, do you know it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10827226 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 I know of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid149840 ED : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2309452\charrsid9112526 It's up Hythe Hill. But then it was known at Barra}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11293696\charrsid9112526 ck}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
